    {
      "title": "Substitute one equation",
      "content": "The second equation gives $x$ in terms of $y$.<br/>$$x=5y$$<br/>Substitute $5y$ for $x$ in the first equation.<br/>$$5y+y=24$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve for both variables",
      "content": "Solve for $y$, then find $x$.<br/>$$6y=24$$<br/>$$y=4$$<br/>$$x=5(4)=20$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Write the ordered pair",
      "content": "The solution is<br/>$$(20,4)$$<br/>The answer is <strong>A</strong>."
